references: Signed copies of original executed lease for space at 4859 Rainier Ave, 525 4th Ave. N and 205 Columbia Street were filed with Clerk's Office on 7-11-94.
summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Department of Administrative Services; amending Seattle Municipal Code (SMC) Section 3.18.200A and SMC 3.18.240 to increase the term and the amount of annual rent per square foot for which non-City-owned properties may be leased by the City.
